data.description: Home On 4 Acres just right outside of city limits. This 4 bedroom 2 bath home with laminate and ceramic tile flooring, lots of storage space, large living room, and bonus room for possible 5 bedroom, this home also offers 2 barns and plenty of space for livestock. Give me a call to schedule your showing today!
